des: Cheeky Radio is a UK based internet station streaming 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. The music policy is Soul, RnB, Jazz-Funk, Soulful House, Reggae, Jazz, Jazzy House and Nu Jazz. The station caters for those who want to expand their knowledge beyond the Anthems & Weekender CDs. We like to do things a bit different at Cheeky Radio. We have a mixture of continuous uninterrupted music for those who just want music, plus a selection of live shows for you to interact with.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
